signature -> @functools.lru_cache(user_function)
brief description -> Decorator to wrap a function with a memoizing callable that saves up to the maxsize most recent calls.
example -> 
```python
@lru_cache
def count_vowels(sentence):
    return sum(sentence.count(vowel) for vowel in 'AEIOUaeiou')
```
